description:
This is a 22 minute workout called 'Legs + Core Row' from the channel James Dietz.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Focus on your form with James as you move through a series of legs-only progressions in Seville. 

Max rhythm: 28, Format: Technique...
